| HistoryText             = 
[[Lorina Dodson (Earth-616)|Lorina Dodson]] established herself as the eccentric criminal the White Rabbit, and assembled a small crew of thugs to begin a criminal career by robbing fast-food restaurants.

During one of the robberies, the gang crossed paths with [[Eugene Patilio (Earth-616)|Frog-Man]], and nearly beat him to death, though he was saved by the timely intervention of [[Peter Parker (Earth-616)|Spider-Man]]. As Dodson escaped, the rest of the crew tried to subdue Spider-Man, to no avail.{{r|Marvel Team-Up Vol 1 131}}
